      "text": "<span class=\"sentence\" id=\"0\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>תַּקִּיפֵאי קַדְמָאֵי, לְעִינְוְותָנֵי בָּתְרָאֵי. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"1\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>דְּתַנְיָא:",
